 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EPerka operates a cardless loyalty mobile application designed to help neighborhood merchants manage profitable long-term customer relationships. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe subscription-based platform includes in-store technology for local small businesses to engage their regular customers and reward authentic purchases. Loyal customers earn perks such as free product or cash discounts by texting from any mobile phone or using the Perka smartphone app. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EA custom-designed Perka loyalty rewards program works every day to help a small business owner encourage repeat customer visits and higher sales, without resorting to the steep discounts of one-time coupons and local daily deals. \u003C/p\u003E",
